T1  - A Methodology for the Study of Organizational Behavior at the Interpersonal Level of Analysis
AU  - Watson, Kathleen M.
Y1  - 1982/07/01
PY  - 1982
DA  - 1982/07/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1982.4285333
