T1  - Business Policy and Metaphysics: Some Philosophical Considerations
AU  - Mitroff, Ian I.
AU  - Mason, Richard O.
Y1  - 1982/07/01
PY  - 1982
DA  - 1982/07/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1982.4285320
